  "prompt": "Where can I get the solutions of resonance sheets and dpps?",
  "response": "Resonance is a well-known coaching institute for engineering and medical entrance exams in India. The solutions to Resonance sheets (study materials) and Daily Practice Problems (DPPs) are often provided to enrolled students through their online learning platforms, student portals, or physical copies distributed in class.\n\nIf you're not enrolled but are looking for solutions, here are some possible approaches:\n\n1. **Official Resonance Website/Portal**: Check if Resonance has made any resources available for free on their official website or student portal.\n\n2. **Online Forums and Educational Websites**: Websites like Gradeup, Byju's, and other educational forums might have these solutions shared by other students.\n\n3. **Social Media Groups and Channels**: Platforms like Telegram, Facebook, and WhatsApp often have groups dedicated to IIT-JEE and NEET preparation where students share study materials and solutions.\n\n4. **Peers and Study Groups**: Connect with friends or other students who are also preparing for these exams. They might have access to these solutions and be willing to share.\n\n5. **Books and Guides**: Some publishers might compile solutions to popular coaching institute materials. Check bookstores or online retailers like Amazon and Flipkart.\n\n6. **Tutors and Coaching Centers**: Local tutors or other coaching centers might have access to these materials and solutions.\n\nRemember, while getting solutions can help you check your work, it\u2019s crucial to attempt problems on your own first to ensure effective learning and understanding.",
